SUMMARY:KY Lake Crappie Circuit - Fall Classic (Chad + Dale)
LOCATION:Kenlake State Resort Park Marina\, 542 Kenlake Rd\, Hardin\, KY 42048
DESCRIPTION:Two-angler team entry. Boat #1974 Dale Venable's 17' Ranger.\n
 Launch 5:30a CT from Kenlake marina ramp 2. Weigh-in 2:00p at pavilion.\n
 Entry paid Sept 22 - $80/team - confirmation KLCC-2026-F-0087.\n
 Team name: Elmwood Two.\n
 Rules briefing 5:00a at the pavilion - Dale said don't be late\, he was late in 2019 and got docked two fish.\n
 Also Chad's 68th birthday - Norma made cake for after weigh-in\, do not tell Dale.\n
 Bring: two rods (jig + minnow)\, tackle box\, PFD\, license (renewed Aug)\, glucose meter\, snacks\, thermos.\nCategories: HEALTH\,FAMILY
